space-amid-rising-tensions-in-west-asia-5431752%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flights-avoid-iranian-airspace-amid-rising-tensions-in-west-asia-5431752%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fair-india-flights-avoid-iranian-airspace-amid-rising-tensions-in-west-asia-5431752%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Terrorists%20Don't%20Play%20By%20Rules%2C%20So%20Response%20Can't%20Have%20Rules%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20that%20India%20was%20committed%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20act%20of%20terrorism%20perpetrated%20from%20across%20the%20borders%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20since%20terrorists%20do%20not%20play%20by%20rules%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20rules%20in%20the%20country's%20answer%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20dispensation%20over%20its%20response%20to%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%202008%2C%20he%20said%20that%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20deliberation%20at%20the%20government%20level%2C%20nothing%20fruitful%20came%20out%20at%20that%20time%20as%20it%20was%20felt%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20attacking%20Pakistan%20was%20more%20than%20not%20attacking%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInteracting%20with%20youth%20on%20Friday%20at%20an%20event%20titled%20'Why%20Bharat%20Matters%3A%20Opportunity%20for%20youth%20and%20participation%20in%20global%20scenario'%20in%20Pune%2C%20he%20asked%20that%20if%20a%20similar%20attack%20happens%20now%20and%20one%20does%20not%20react%20to%20it%2C%20how%20can%20the%20next%20such%20attacks%20be%20prevented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20said%20that%20the%20country's%20foreign%20policy%20has%20undergone%20a%20change%20since%202014%20and%20it%20is%20the%20way%20terrorism%20is%20dealt%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20countries%20with%20which%20India%20finds%20it%20challenging%20to%20maintain%20relationships%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20should%20question%20whether%20it%20should%20maintain%20any%20relationship%20with%20certain%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20one%20is%20just%20next%20to%20us.%20Let%20us%20be%20honest%2C%20the%20one%20country%20that%20is%20very%2C%20very%20difficult%20is%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20for%20that%2C%20we%20should%20only%20introspect%20why.%20One%20reason%20for%20this%20is%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20had%20India%20been%20clear%20from%20the%20start%20that%20Pakistan%20was%20indulging%20in%20terrorism%2C%20which%20India%20should%20not%20tolerate%20under%20any%20circumstances%2C%20the%20country%20would%20have%20had%20a%20vastly%20different%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20Modi%20ji%20came.%20But%20this%20problem%20(terrorism)%20did%20not%20start%20in%202014.%20It%20did%20not%20begin%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20attack.%20It%20happened%20in%201947.%20In%201947%2C%20the%20first%20people%20(invaders)%20came%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20they%20attacked%20Kashmir.%20It%20was%20an%20act%20of%20terrorism.%20They%20were%20burning%20down%20villages%20and%20towns.%20They%20were%20killing%20people.%20These%20people%20were%20tribals%20from%20Pakistan's%20North-West%20Frontier%20Province.%20The%20Pakistan%20army%20backed%20them.%20We%20sent%20the%20army%2C%20and%20the%20integration%20of%20Kashmir%20took%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20Indian%20army%20was%20taking%20action%2C%20we%20stopped%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20went%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20mentioning%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20by%20tribal%20invaders%20instead%20of%20terrorism%2C%20as%20if%20it%20was%20a%20legitimate%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20the%201965%20Indo-Pak%20war%2C%20Pakistan%20first%20sent%20infiltrators%20to%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20very%20clear%20in%20our%20minds%20about%20terrorism%3B%20under%20no%20circumstances%20is%20terrorism%20acceptable%20from%20any%20neighbour%20or%20from%20anyone%20who%20uses%20terrorism%20to%20force%20you%20to%20sit%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%20This%20should%20never%20be%20accepted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mentioned%20that%20sometimes%20he%20is%20asked%20about%20the%20continuity%20in%20India's%20foreign%20policy%20and%20he%20responds%20clearly%20that%20there%20is%2050%20per%20cent%20continuity%20and%2050%20per%20cent%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20change%20is%20regarding%20terrorism.%20After%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attack%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20single%20person%20in%20the%20country%20who%20felt%20that%20we%20should%20not%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20attack.%20Everybody%20in%20the%20country%20felt%20it.%20There%20is%20an%20account%20of%20that%20time.%20The%20NSA%20had%20written%20that%20this%20minister%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20that%20minister%20looked%20at%20it.%20Everybody%20deliberated%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20analysis%20took%20place%2C%20and%20then%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20attacking%20Pakistan%20is%20more%20than%20not%20attacking%20Pakistan.%20So%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20deliberation%2C%20nothing%20fruitful%20came%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20if%20something%20like%20Mumbai%20happens%20and%20you%20do%20not%20react%20to%20it%2C%20how%20can%20you%20prevent%20the%20next%20one%20from%20happening%3F%20%26quot%3BThey%20(terrorists)%20should%20not%20feel%20that%20since%20they%20are%20across%20the%20border%2C%20no%20one%20can%20touch%20them.%20Terrorists%20do%20not%20play%20by%20any%20rules.%20The%20response%20to%20terrorists%20cannot%20have%20any%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712987760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fkjhcoll_s-jaishankar-ani_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-dont-play-by-rules-so-response-cant-have-rules-s-jaishankar-5429572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20that%20India%20was%20committed%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20act%20of%20terrorism%20perpetrated%20from%20across%20the%20borders%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20since%20terrorists%20do%20not%20play%20by%20rules%2C%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20rules%20in%20the%20country's%20answer%20to%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-dont-play-by-rules-so-response-cant-have-rules-s-jaishankar-5429572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-dont-play-by-rules-so-response-cant-have-rules-s-jaishankar-5429572%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-dont-play-by-rules-so-response-cant-have-rules-s-jaishankar-5429572%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20hails%20work%20to%20reduce%20racial%20wealth%20gap%20as%20he%20seeks%20voter%20support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712987670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109264003%2Cimgsize-834783.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbiden-hails-work-to-reduce-racial-wealth-gap-as-he-seeks-voter-support%2Farticleshow%2F109263775.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109263775.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBiden%20discusses%20progress%20and%20challenges%20in%20closing%20the%20racial