u's%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20blast%20case%2C%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20West%20Bengal%20yesterday%2C%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20a%20Bengaluru%20court%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdbul%20Matheen%20Ahmed%20Taahaa%20and%20Mussavir%20Hussain%20Shazib%20were%20brought%20to%20Bengaluru%20late%20last%20evening%20after%20their%20arrest%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShazeb%20and%20Taha%20were%20traced%20to%20Kanthi%2C%20or%20Contai%2C%20a%20small%20city%20180%20km%20from%20Kolkata%2C%20after%20officials%20conducted%20searches%20at%2018%20locations%20across%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Adbul%20Matheen%20Ahmed%20Taahaa%20and%20Mussavir%20Hussain%20Shazib%2C%20had%20been%20staying%20in%20a%20lodge%20in%20Bengal%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20in%20Kolkata%20had%20yesterday%20granted%20a%203-day%20transit%20remand%20to%20the%20two%20men%2C%20allowing%20the%20NIA%20to%20take%20them%20to%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaahaa%20was%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%20blast%20while%20Shazib%20placed%20the%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Device%20(IED)%20at%20the%20cafe%2C%26quot%3B%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20men%20were%20on%20the%20run%20since%20the%20explosion%20rocked%20the%20popular%20Bengaluru%20cafe%20on%20March%201%2C%20leaving%2010%20people%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20Abdul%20Matheen%20who%20also%20worked%20on%20the%20escape%20plans%20and%20managed%20to%20evade%20arrest%20all%20these%20weeks.%20The%20duo%2C%20along%20with%20their%20co-accused%20Maaz%20Muneer%20Ahmed%2C%20were%20also%20involved%20in%20terror%20cases%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NIA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20took%20over%20the%20probe%20on%20March%203%20and%20had%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20each%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%2C%20which%20suffered%20extensive%20damage%20after%20the%20blast%2C%20reopened%20eight%20days%20later%2C%20with%20enhanced%20security%20measures%20including%20metal%20detectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20strengthened%20our%20security%20team%20and%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20set%20up%20a%20separate%20panel%20of%20ex-servicemen%20who%20will%20train%20security%20guards%20at%20all%20our%20branches%2C%26quot%3B%20co-founder%20Raghavendra%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712982720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2b81a8u_bengaluru-blast-suspects-650-_650x400_12_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-key-accused-in-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-brought-to-bengaluru-after-arrest-in-bengal-5431203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20key%20accused%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Rameshwaram%20Cafe%20blast%20case%2C%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20West%20Bengal%20yesterday%2C%20will%20be%20produced%20in%20a%20Bengaluru%20court%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-key-accused-in-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-brought-to-bengaluru-after-arrest-in-bengal-5431203%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-key-accused-in-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-brought-to-bengaluru-after-arrest-in-bengal-5431203%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-key-accused-in-rameshwaram-cafe-blast-brought-to-bengaluru-after-arrest-in-bengal-5431203%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20India's%20156.6%20Kmph%20Pace%20Sensation%20Mayank%20Shouldn't%20Be%20Picked%20For%20T20%20WC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%20one-third%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024%20season%20is%20done%20and%20dusted%20and%20like%20always%2C%20the%20competition%20has%20already%20unearthed%20some%20gems%20from%20the%20domestic%20circuit.%20Apart%20from%20the%20batting%20pyrotechnics%20by%20Shashank%20Singh%20and%20Ashutosh%20Sharma%2C%20India%20has%20also%20discovered%20a%20bowler%20with%20raw%20pace%20in%20Mayank%20Yadav%2C%20who%20has%20grabbed%20eyeballs%20in%20IPL%202024%20having%20consistently%20clocked%20deliveries%20over%20150%20kmph.%20He%20also%20bowled%20the%20fastest%20ball%20of%20the%20season%20at%20156.7%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20pacer%20from%20Delhi%20won%20two%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20awards%20in%20his%20first%20two%20games%20for%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20(LSG)%2C%20with%20most%20of%20his%20deliveries%20clocking%20north%20of%20150%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20Mayank%20has%20put%20his%20name%20in%20the%20reckoning%20for%20India's%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20after%20his%20match-winning%20three-fers%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20pacer%20is%20currently%20injured%20and%20will%20miss%20at%20least%20LSG's%20next%20two%20fixtures%20due%20to%20soreness%20in%20his%20lower%20abdominal%20area.%20%26quot%3BHe%20felt%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20tightness%20at%20the%20top%20of%20his%20hip%20leading%20into%20the%20last%20game%2C%20but%20that%20was%20about%20a%20one-out-of-ten%20pain%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20that%20there%20were%20clinical%20signs%2C%26quot%3B%20LSG%20head%20coach%20Justin%20Langer%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20April%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20note%20that%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20is%20just%20around%20the%20corner%20and%20India%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20marquee%20ICC%20event%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20USA%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Mohammed%20Shami%20out%20of%20contention%20due%20to%20injury%20and%20a%20few%20other%20experienced%20fast%20bowlers%20like%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20and%20Harshal%20Patel%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20this%20year's%20IPL%2C%20the%20question%20on%20everyone's%20mind%20is%20whether%20Mayank%20Yadav%20deserves%20a%20place%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mayank%20has%20captured%20the%20collective%20imagination%20of%20the%20cricketing%20fraternity%20in%20the%20country%20with%20his%20express%20pace%2C%20whether%20the%20pacer%20deserves%20to%20be%20picked%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20still%20up%20for%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20let's%20take%20a%20look%20at%20if%20Mayank%20Yadav%20does%20indeed%20deserve%20a%20place%20in%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20WC%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Mayank%20Yadav%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%2C%20who%20represents%20Delhi%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%2C%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20former%20Indian%20player%20Vijay%20Dahiya%20during%20a%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%20game.%20Given%20this%20happened%20just%20before%20the%20IPL%20mega%20auction%202022%2C%20the%20youngster%20was%20snapped%20up%20by%20LSG%20with%20Dahiya%20being%20their%20assistant%20coach%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20did%20not%20play%20a%20match%20in%20the%20first%20season%20and%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20next%20campaign%20with%20a%20torn%20hamstring.%20However%2C%20Mayank%20performed%20well%20for%20Delhi%20and%20North%20Zone%20in%20the%20white%20ball%20format%20in%20domestic%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20picked%20up%20five%20wickets%20in%20four%20games%20in%20the%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy%202023-24%20for%20Delhi%20and%20also%20returned%20with%20six%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20in%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicked%20in%20the%20North%20Zone%20squad%2C%20Mayank%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performers%20in%20the%202023%20Deodhar%20Trophy.%20He%20ended%20up%20with%2012%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2017.58.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%20though%2C%20Mayank%20has%20played%20only%20one%20first-class%20game%20in%20his%20young%20career.%20His%20Ranji%20Trophy%20debut%20came%20against%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20he%20scalped%20two%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20track%20two%20years%20after%20initially%20being%20bought%20by%20LSG%20and%20Mayank%20impressed%20one%20and%20all%20straightaway%20on%20his%20IPL%20debut%20against%20PBKS%20as%20he%20bagged%20a%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20award%20following%20an%20impressive%20spell%20of%203%20for%2027%20which%20helped%20Lucknow%20win%20a%20crucial%20home%20fixture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20he%20probably%20still%20hasn't%20done%20enough%20to%20bag%20a%20spot%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20as%20a%20fast%20bowler%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20area%20where%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20have%20fallen%20short%20in%20past%20ICC%20tournaments%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Mayank%20Yadav%20should%20not%20be%20picked%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20knowledge%20by%20now%20that%20India%20has%20not%20won%20an%20ICC%20trophy%20since%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202013%20and%20their%20bowling%20attack%20has%20not%20helped%20the%20team's%20cause%20in%20ending%20the%20trophy%20drought%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20strongest%20national%20sides%20since%20their%20memorable%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20victory%20in%202011.%20After%20that%20tournament%20win%20at%20home%2C%20India%20has%20participated%20in%20five%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20their%20record%20in%20those%20ICC%20events%20doesn't%20make%20for%20kind%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20performance%20in%20T20%20WCs%20since%202011%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2012%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20-%20Super%20Eight%20stage%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2014%20in%20Bangladesh%20-%20Runners-up%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2016%20in%20India%20-%20Semi-finals%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2021%20in%20the%20UAE%20-%20Group%20stage%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2022%20in%20Australia%20-%20Semi-finals%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20India%20lost%20all%20three%20of%20their%20T20%20World%20Cup%20knockout%20matches%20since%20then%20by%20failing%20to%20defend%20targets%20-%20in%202014%20(lost%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20the%20Final%20by%206%20wickets)%2C%20in%202016%20(lost%20to%20West%20Indies%20in%20the%20semi-final%20by%207%20wickets)%2C%20and%20in%202022%20(lost%20to%20England%20in%20the%20semi-final%20by%2010%20wickets).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20India's%20only%20loss%20against%20Pakistan%20came%20in%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20game%20in%202021%20when%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20failed%20to%20defend%20a%20152-run%20target%20and%20suffered%20a%2010-wicket%20defeat%20as%20experienced%20bowlers%20like%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20and%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%20struggled%20to%20thwart%20the%20Pakistani%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20hence%20safe%20to%20say%20that%20even%20experienced%20Indian%20bowlers%20have%20struggled%20to%20produce%20their%20best%20in%20crunch%20situations%20in%20ICC%20tournaments%20over%20the%20years.%20Add%20to%20that%2C%20Mayank's%20inexperience%20even%20in%20India's%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20one%20can%20imagine%20why%20picking%20the%2021-year-old%20speedster%20comes%20with%20huge%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20past%20experiences%20of%20fast-tracking%20speedsters%20like%20Umran%20Malik%20to%20the%20senior%20Indian%20squad%20on%20the%20back%20of%20strong%20IPL%20performances%20haven't%20always%20worked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Mayank%2C%20Umran%20Malik%20was%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town%20thanks%20to%20solid%20IPL%20performances%20but%20upon%20being%20selected%20for%20the%20national%20team%2C%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20pacer%20failed%20to%20live%20up%20to%20his%20billing%20and%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20action%20on%20the%20international%20stage%20in%20July%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20only%20limited%20pace%20bowling%20slots%20to%20fill%20doesn't%20help%20Mayank%20Yadav's%20case%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20T20%20WC%202024%20squad%20either%20since%20it%20could%20prove%20costly%20for%20India%2C%20considering%20his%20lack%20of%20experience%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20think%20tank%20also%20has%20proven%20talents%20in%20the%20T20%20stage%20in%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Avesh%20Khan%2C%20and%20Deepak%20Chahar%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20And%20while%20a%20raw%20talent%20like%20Mayank%20Yadav%20is%20bound%20to%20don%20national%20colours%20soon%2C%20perhaps%20adding%20him%20to%20the%202024%20T20%20squad%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20good%20performances%20is%20a%20step%20too%20far%20in%20his%20still%20nascent%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712982660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F7cg44cs_mayank-yadav-bcci_625x300_31_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fwhy-indias-156-6-kmph-pace-sensation-mayank-yadav-should-not-be-picked-for-t20-world-cup-5428046%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mayank%20Yadav%20has%20only%20played%20one%20first-class%20game%20in%20his%20young%20career%20till%20date.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Federal%20judge%20denies%20Hunter%20Biden's%20motion%20to%20dismiss%20gun%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712982551000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109262091%2Cimgsize-1443422.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffederal-judge-denies-hunter-bidens-motion-to-dismiss-gun-charges%2Farticleshow%2F109262120.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C