20identity%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20posts%2C%20Mr%20Rowling%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20been%20criticised%20for%20anti-transgender%20comments%2C%20shared%20a%20recent%20independent%20review%20%26quot%3Bof%20the%20medical%20evidence%20for%20transitioning%20children%26quot%3B.%20One%20follower%20responded%20to%20her%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20waiting%20for%20Dan%20and%20Emma%20to%20give%20you%20a%20very%20public%20apology%20...%20safe%20in%20the%20knowledge%20that%20you%20will%20forgive%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20this%2C%20Ms%20Rowling%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20safe%2C%20I'm%20afraid.%20Celebs%20who%20cosied%20up%20to%20a%20movement%20intent%20on%20eroding%20women's%20hard-won%20rights%20and%20who%20used%20their%20platforms%20to%20cheer%20on%20the%20transitioning%20of%20minors%20can%20save%20their%20apologies%20for%20traumatised%20detransitioners%20and%20vulnerable%20women%20reliant%20on%20single%20sex%20spaces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENot%20safe%2C%20I'm%20afraid.%20Celebs%20who%20cosied%20up%20to%20a%20movement%20intent%20on%20eroding%20women's%20hard-won%20rights%20and%20who%20used%20their%20platforms%20to%20cheer%20on%20the%20transitioning%20of%20minors%20can%20save%20their%20apologies%20for%20traumatised%20detransitioners%20and%20vulnerable%20women%20reliant%20on%20single%20sex%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20J.K.%20Rowling%20(%40jk_rowling)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjk_rowling%2Fstatus%2F1778124467027267804%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJK%20Rowling's%20Fall%20Out%20With%20Daniel%20Radcliffe%20And%20Emma%20Watson%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJK%20Rowling%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20transphobic%20for%20her%20views%20on%20gender%20identity%20and%20for%20saying%20trans%20wo