0well%20over%20a%20half-billion-dollars%20in%20judgments%20against%20him.%20Trump%20has%20posted%20bonds%20covering%20both%20judgments%20while%20he%20appeals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20those%20two%20matters%2C%20he%20was%20personally%20responsible%20for%20generating%20much%2C%20if%20not%20most%2C%20of%20the%20surrounding%20publicity%20with%20his%20public%20statements%2C%20which%20were%20often%20made%20just%20a%20few%20steps%20outside%20the%20courtroom%20where%20the%20proceedings%20were%20being%20conducted%2C%20and%20with%20his%20unrelenting%20media%20posts%20attacking%20those%20he%20perceived%20to%20be%20responsible%20for%20his%20plight%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20Defendant%20finds%20himself%20in%20now%20is%20not%20new%20to%20him%20and%20at%20least%20in%20part%2C%20of%20his%20own%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20attorneys%20Susan%20Necheles%20and%20Todd%20Blanche%20had%20argued%20that%20%26quot%3Bprejudicial%20media%20coverage%20has%20saturated%20the%20venire%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20jury%20pool%2C%20and%20that%20Manhattan%20is%20%26quot%3Boverwhelmingly%20biased%26quot%3B%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20a%20fair%20jury%20could%20not%20be%20chosen%20any%20time%20in%20April%2C%20and%20asked%20Merchan%20to%20delay%20the%20trial%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump's%20Constitutional%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial%20is%20at%20stake%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20defense%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24522387-ny-v-trump-defense-adjournment-motion-20240318%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20March%2018%20delay%20motion%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20included%20180%20pages%20of%20supporting%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense-hired%20pollsters%20found%20that%2061%25%20of%20Manhattan%20potential%20jurors%20already%20believe%20Trump%20is%20guilty%20of%20%3Cem%3Esomething%3C%2Fem