0easily%20be%20an%20around-the-house%20shoe%20with%20how%20easily%20they%20slip%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20put%20them%20on%2C%20I%20already%20had%20blisters%20from%20wearing%20new%20boots%20with%20the%20wrong%20socks%20(my%20own%20fault).%20Rothy's%20loafers%20were%20gentle%20on%20my%20tender%20heels%2C%20as%20my%20Band-Aided%20skin%20lay%20flush%20against%20the%20flexible%20mesh%20so%20there%20was%20no%20added%20friction.%20After%20I'd%20healed%2C%20the%20Loafers%20didn't%20cause%20me%20any%20more%20blistering.%20As%20an%208%2C%20these%20fit%20me%20true%20to%20size%2C%20but%20they%20do%20have%20a%20relatively%20narrow%20toe%20box.%20For%20this%20reason%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20them%20for%20wider%20feet%2C%20or%20else%20the%20outline%20of%20your%20toes%20will%20likely%20be%20visible%20through%20the%20stretchy%20knit%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Loafer%20comes%20in%20six%20colors.%20Their%20simple%20design%20and%20muted%20colorways%20go%20with%20just%20about%20everything%20in%20my%20closet.%20I'd%20had%20this%20green%20skirt%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20could%20never%20find%20the%20right%20shoe%20to%20match.%20Finally%2C%20Rothy's%20to%20the%20rescue.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Gabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Associate%20Style%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Almond%20Loafer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222171%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20loafers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651ae9a703971f0019320f84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERothy's%20The%20Almond%20Loafer%20in%20Desert%20Cat.%3Cp%3EMaiya%20Pascouche%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20with%20feet%20on%20the%20wider%20side%2C%20I%20was%20a%20little%20nervous%20about%20these%20pointed-toe%20loafers.%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20chance%20because%20they%20describe%20the%20%26quot%3Balmond-toe%20profile%26quot%3B%20as%20a%