I%20was%20able%20to%20wear%20them%20for%20a%20full%20day%20without%20any%20break%20in%20period.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Gabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Associate%20Style%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Square%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20leopard%20print%20flats%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor%20next%20to%20someone%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20leopard%20print%20flats.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aeda64ff1e30019477146%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERothy's%20The%20Square%20in%20Desert%20Cat.%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Square%20has%20a%20silhouette%20that%20feels%20like%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20the%20Point%20and%20the%20Flat%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20ready%20to%20commit%20to%20either%20of%20those%20shapes.%20These%20are%20the%20best%20pair%20for%20people%20with%20wider%20feet%20out%20of%20all%20Rothy's%20ballet%20flat%20styles%2C%20due%20to%20the%20spacious%20toe%20box%20that%20tapers%20to%20a%20generous%20square%20tip.%20My%20narrow%20foot%20slips%20right%20into%20these%20and%20they%20stay%20put%2C%20but%20the%20unique%20recycled%20plastic%20knit%20is%20perfectly%20capable%20of%20stretching.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Squares%20come%20in%20five%20colorways%2C%20of%20which%20I%20chose%20the%20Desert%20Cat.%20Before%20this%20Rothy's%20review%2C%20my%20one%20surviving%20pair%20of%20flats%20were%20from%20Target%20(also%20leopard%20print).%20I%20lost%20those%20when%20I%20got%20caught%20in%20the%20rain%20and%20they%20were%20past%20salvaging.%20So%20while%20Rothy's%20are%20much%20more%20of%20an%20investment%2C%20the%20durability%20and%20washability%20assures%20me%20I%20won't%20have%20to%20ever%20suddenly%20trash%20them.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94Gabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Associate%20Style%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Square%20Mary%20Jane%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20black%20Mary%20Jane%20flats%20next%20to%20someone%20wearing%20a%20pair%20of%20black%20Mary%20Jane%20flats%20over%20long%20socks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651aeef3ecc9f4001942a499%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Square%20Mary%20Janes%20in%20black.%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERothy's%20Mary%20Janes%20are%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20my%20wardrobe%20because%20I%20personally%20like%20a%20little%20feminine%20flair.%20But%20the%20thin%20band%20across%20the%20middle%20does%20seem%20like%20a%20design%20afterthought.%20It%20only%20transforms%20the%20silhouette%20from%20a%20regular%20flat%20to%20a%20Mary%20Jane%20on%20a%20very%20literal%20level.%20The%20tabs%20at%20each%20end%20would%20probably%20look%20better%20if%20they%20were%20stitched%20right%20into%20the%20upper%20so%20they%20don't%20stick%20out.%20However%2C%20if%20you're%20going%20for%20the%20twee%20look%2C%20I%20think%20the%20benefits%20of%20wearing%20Rothy's%20greatly%20outweigh%20a%20more%20expensive%2C%20less%20sustainable%2C%20and%20ultimately%20less%20comfortable%20pair%20of%20leather%20Mary%20Janes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20pair%20these%20with%20ankle%20socks%20or%20even%20knee%20highs%20and%20they%20have%20more%20of%20a%20ballerina%20feel%20than%20a%20chunky%20platform%20will.%20They%20have%20a%20relatively%20narrow%20toe%20box%2C%20but%20having%20narrow%20feet%2C%20they%20contoured%20to%20my%20foot%20easily.%20I%20felt%20these%20fit%20me%20true%20to%20size%2C%20but%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20style%20these%20with%20thick%20socks%2C%20I'd%20go%20up%20half%20a%20size.%20%E2%80%94%3Cem%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2C%20Associate%20Style%20Editor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lightweight%20Mega%20Tote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%2C%20a%20tote%20bag%20stuffed%20with%20shoes%20and%20sweaters.%20Right%2C%20a%20model%20wears%20a%20tote%20on%20shoulder.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554d73d22cf74a573979f68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERothy%E2%80%99s%20The%20Lightweight%20Mega%20Tote%20in%20Navy%20Twill.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20fill%20mine%20with%20eight%20pairs%20of%20shoes%20and%20a%20bundle%20of%20sweaters.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20oversized%20totes%20I've%20ever%20used.%20The%20design%20is%20so%20elegant%20and%20simple%2C%20but%20there%20are%20so%20many%20thoughtful%20details%20in%20the%20design%20that%20make%20it%20worth%20the%20investment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20straps%20are%20actually%20long%20enough%20to%20sling%20the%20whole%20bag%20over%20your%20shoulder%20and%20they%20have%20slightly%20rounded%20edges%20so%20they%20don't%20dig%20in%20uncomfortably.%20Second%2C%20not%20that%20you'll%20ever%20be%20putting%20this%20much%20weight%20in%20a%20tote%2C%20but%20Rothy's%20claims%20this%20bag%20holds%20up%20to%20150%20lbs.%20I%20haven't%20weight-tested%20it%20to%20quite%20that%20degree%2C%20but%20I%20can%20at%20least%20corroborate%20their%20claim%20that%20the%20bag%20is%20very%20sturdy%20after%20packing%20it%20with%20a%20picnic%20for%20four%20and%20lugging%20it%20onto%20a%20boat.%20Third%2C%20I%20wasn't%20worried%20about%20it%20getting%20wet%20or%20dirty%20because%20it%20dries%20pretty%20quickly%20and%20can%20be%20thrown%20in%20the%20washing%20machine.%20(Yes%2C%20I%20said%20thrown%20in%20the%20washing%20machine!)%20And%20fourth%2C%20there%20are%20key%20straps%20on%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20tote%20along%20with%20a%20small%20patch%20attached%20to%20the%20interior%20wall%20so%20that%20small%20essentials%20won't%20get%20lost%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bag.%20All%20in%20all%2