%20on%20to%20this%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20disheartened.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20climatic%20conditions%20of%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20India%20are%20the%20same%2C%20so%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20cultivate%20dates%20ourselves%3F%20We%20should%20lose%20some%20of%20the%20dependency%20on%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelieving%20this%20as%20his%20patriotic%20duty%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335795%2Fisro-project-scientist-divakar-channappa-first-organic-date-farmer-in-karnataka-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecultivate%20dates%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Pilani.%20Last%20season%2C%20Mukesh%20harvested%20five%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20dates%20which%20earned%20him%20a%20huge%20income%20of%20Rs%2012%20lakh.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20his%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20commando%20to%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20up%20date%20farming%2C%20Mukesh%20worked%20as%20a%20commando%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%2015%20years.%20He%20specialised%20in%20counter-hijack%20operations%20to%20safeguard%20people.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20took%20voluntary%20retirement%20from%20the%20NSG%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20work%2C%20I%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20visit%2020%20countries.%20On%20my%20way%20from%20the%20airports%20to%20hotels%2C%20I%20would%20spare%20some%20time%20to%20visit%20nearby%20farms%20and%20learn%20about%20their%20technologies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAgriculture%20is%20in%20my%20DNA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20my%20father%20and%20grandfathers%20grow%20crops.%20But%20like%20them%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20grow%20traditional%20crops%20like%20mustard%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20grams