ing%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20on%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%203-day%20training%20programme%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Excellence%20for%20Date%20Palm%20at%20Sagra-Bhojka%20in%20the%20Jaisalmer%20district.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20the%20state%20government%20was%20promoting%20date%20cultivation%20in%20Rajasthan%20by%20distributing%20subsidised%20date%20palm%20saplings%20to%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20procured%20250%20date%20palm%20seeds%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342788%2Fyellow-dates-farming-in-india-engineer-quits-job-to-become-an-agripreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyellow-coloured%20Barhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20red-coloured%20Khuneji%20varieties%20and%20planted%20them%20on%20his%20farmland.%20It%20took%20four%20years%20before%20he%20saw%20the%20first%20fruit%20on%20the%20date%20palm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20grow%20money%20on%20trees%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20points%20out%20that%20growing%20dates%20have%20been%20extremely%20fruitful%20as%20both%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20plant%20say%20100%20trees%2C%20then%20only%201-2%20will%20die.%20The%20remaining%20trees%20will%20survive%20and%20continue%20to%20yield%20for%2080%20years.%20Besides%2C%20once%20the%20seeds%20are%20sown%2C%20we%20are%20only%20required%20to%20provide%20organic%20manures%20like%20cow%20and%20goat%20dung.%20Every%20year%2C%20I%20just%20add%20150%20kg%20of%20manure%20to%20one%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-4-17125