20for%20their%20town%20municipal%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20goes%20on%20to%20elaborate%20on%20other%20such%20projects%20his%20trust%20has%20embarked%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20claims%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Devanahalli%20township%2C%20where%20the%20international%20airport%20is%20located%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20work%20with%20several%20NGOs%20and%20partners%20who%20cleaned%20up%20a%20lake%2C%20which%20is%20now%20filled%20with%20rainwater%20and%20well-treated%20wastewater%20from%20Bengaluru.%20This%20water%20filters%20into%20the%20earth%20and%20there%20is%20an%20old%20open%20well%20we%20have%20revived.%20That%20well%20gives%202.5%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20a%20day%20to%20which%20we%20have%20attached%20a%20water%20treatment%20plant%20and%20are%20supplying%20that%20water%20to%20the%20town%20of%20Devanahalli.%20We%20have%20also%20constructed%20filter%20borewells%2C%20which%20are%20shallow%20borewells%20which%20go%2080%20to%20100%20feet%20deep%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20porous%20casing%20and%20function%20like%20open%20recharge%20wells.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20we%20do%20good%20%5Bopen%5D%20recharge%20%5Bwells%5D%20and%20lakes%20are%20revived%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20shallow%20aquifer%20which%20comes%20back%20to%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FeXn1Lx725Js%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcol