een%20demand%20and%20supply.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20groundwater%20cell%20in%20the%20BWSSB%20or%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20groundwater%20plan%20or%20an%20aquifer%20management%20plan%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20everyone%20is%20tapping%20into%20the%20aquifer%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20are%20seeing%20today%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20competitive%20drilling.%20In%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20people%20have%20dug%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%201%2C800%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CEverybody%20is%20taking%20water%20out.%20Nobody%20is%20putting%20water%20back%20in.%20Unless%20we%20create%20the%20right%20type%20of%20institution%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20groundwater%20and%20manages%20it%20as%20a%20common%20pool%20resource%20for%20all%20citizens%2C%20this%20is%20what%20will%20happen%20and%20is%20happening.%20The%20problem%20is%20institutional%20and%20lies%20in%20governance%20or%20lack%20thereof%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20959px)%20100vw%2C%20959px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Can%20we%20solve%20Bengaluru's%20Water%20scarcity%20problem%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034.jpg%20959w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-500x330.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FS-Vishwanath-Lake-Water-1-1712316034-768x507.jpg%20768w%2C%