0rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20their%20open%20recharge%20wells%20are%20giving%20them%20two%20lakh%20litres%20of%20water%20a%20day.%20At%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267840%2Fiim-cat-tips-tricks-hacks-things-to-know-work-experience-selection-process-quora%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIM%20Bangalore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20rainwater%20harvesting%20has%20been%20done%2C%20their%20borewells%20are%20giving%20them%20water%20at%20300%20to%20400%20feet%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20getting%20enough%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWherever%20rainwater%20harvesting%20is%20done%20well%20and%20in%20concentrated%20amounts%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20problem.%20Their%20aquifers%20are%20full%20and%20have%20water%20despite%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20drought.%20Even%20in%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20where%20people%20and%20organisations%20have%20done%20rainwater%20harvesting%20like%20Friends%20of%20Lakes%2C%20there%20is%20water%20in%20open%20recharge%20wells.%20Rainwater%20harvesting%20can%20send%20in%20X%20amount%20of%20water%20but%20your%20withdrawal%20should%20be%20less%20than%20X.%20If%20your%20draw%20is%202X%2C%20then%20even%20this%20won%E2%80%99t%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20there%20are%20more%20concerns%20about%20the%20rainwater%20harvesting%20(RWH)%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20city.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20BWSSB%20Amendment%20Act%2C%202011%2C%20made%20RWH%20mandatory%20for%20all%20properties%20on%20plots%20measuring%2060%C3%9740%20sq%20ft%20and%20above%2C%20and%20new%20properties%20coming%20up%20on%2030%C3%9740%20sq%20ft%20sites.%20In%202015%2C%20penalties%20were%20introduced%20for%20properties%20that%20didn%E2%80%99t%20comply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%207%20December%202023%20report%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcitizenmatters.in%2Fbengaluru-rainwater-harvesting-bwssb-kscst-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitizen%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20media%20publication%2C%20reporter%20Navya%20PK%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20city%20currently%20has%2010.8%20lakh%20properties%20with%20water%20connections%2C%20but%20only%201.9%20lakh%20(nearly%2018%25)%20of%20them%20have%20implemented%20RWH.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%2039%2C703%20properties%20have%20been%20identified%20for%20non-implementation%20and%20are%20paying%20penalties%20every%20month.%20These%20properties%20include%20individual%20homes%2C%20apartments%20(each%20apartment%20is%20counted%20as%20a%20single%20connection)%2C%20and%20commercial%20properties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20compliance%20is%20a%20serious%20issue%20even%20though%20installing%20a%20RWH%20system%20is%20neither%20very%20complicated%20nor%20cost-intensive.%20Vishwanath%20notes%20that%20residents%20should%20build%20robust%20RWH%20systems%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20face%20quality-related%20concerns%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20that%20there%20are%20enough%20quality%20materials%20and%20competent%20plumbers%20present%20in%20the%20market.%20An%20individual%20home%20can%20install%20a%20RWH%20system%20for%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%205%2C000.%20Even%20if%20you%20insist%20on%20using%20a%20high-quality%20filter%2C%20it%20can%20be%20done%20within%20Rs%2015%2C000%2C%20provided%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20build%20a%20new%20sump%2C%20he%20argues.%20And%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20system%20are%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20home%2C%20we%20have%20rainwater%20harvesting%20systems%20that%20are%20operating%20optimally.%20Even%20though%20the%20last%20rains%20in%20the%20city%20were%20in%20November%2C%20our%201%2C000-litre%20rain%20barrel%20still%20has%20enough%20water%20for%20our%20drinking%20and%20cooking%20needs%20till%20June%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20compliance%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbangaloremirror.indiatimes.com%2Fbangalore%2Fothers%2Fare-you-harvesting-rainwater%2Farticleshow%2F106646319.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBangalore%20Mirror%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20by%20Sridhar%20Vivan%20on%209%20January%202024%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20staggering%20Rs%2021.24%20crore%20was%20collected%20as%20penalties%20for%20non-compliance%20with%20rainwater%20harvesting%20regulations%20until%20November-end%20last%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20non-implementation%20of%20RWH%20in%20residential%20properties%2C%20fines%20start%20from%2025%25%20of%20their%20water%20bill%20for%20the%20first%20three%20months%2C%20and%2050%25%20afterwards.%20For%20non-residential%20properties%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%2050%25%20and%20100%25%20of%20the%20water%20bill%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20argues%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20expect%20100%25%20compliance%20and%20argues%20that%20penalising%20residents%20may%20not%20be%20the%20way%20forward.%20Instead%2C%20he%20recommends%20that%20people%20should%20want%20to%20set%20up%20a%20RWH%20system%20in%20their%20homes%20after%20a%20process%20of%20education%20and%20communication.%20And%20the%20benefits%20of%20installing%20such%20a%20system%20in%20each%20Bengaluru%20home%20would%20be%20immense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Datajam%20organised%20last%20month%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopencity.in%2Fbengaluru-water-datajam-march-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpen%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20civic%20tech%20project%2C%20found%20that%20based%20on%20rainfall%20data%20from%202022%2C%20%E2%80%9C456%20Milli